#: base/configurations/default_setting.py:201
msgid ""
"Require attendees to fill in postal addresses for all admission tickets."
msgstr "Kræv, at deltagere udfylder postadresser for alle adgangsbilletter."

#: base/configurations/default_setting.py:212
msgid ""
"Ask for an email address per order. The order confirmation will be sent to "
