#: base/models/settings.py:71
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"we hope you’re happy with eventyay as your event’s CfP system.\n"
"These links may be helpful in the coming days and weeks:\n"
"\n"
"- Your event’s dashboard: {event_dashboard}\n"
"- A list of proposals: {event_submissions}\n"
"- Your schedule editor: {event_schedule}\n"
"\n"
"If there is anything you’re missing, please contact us via our website on "
"eventyay.com.\n"
msgstr ""
"Hej,\n"
"\n"
"vi håber, at du er tilfreds med eventyay som CfP-system til dit "
"arrangement.\n"
"Disse links kan være nyttige i de kommende dage og uger:\n"
"\n"
"- Dit arrangements dashboard: {event_dashboard}\n"
"- En liste over forslag: {event_submissions}\n"
"- Din skemaredigering: {event_schedule}\n"
"\n"
"Hvis der er noget, der mangler, kan du kontakte os via vores hjemmeside på "
"eventyay.com.\n"

#: base/models/settings.py:90
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"just writing you to let you know that your Call for Participation is now\n"
"closed. Here is a list of links that should be useful in the next days:\n"
"\n"
"- You’ll find a list of all your {submission_count} proposals here:\n"
"  {event_submissions}\n"
"- You can add reviewers here:\n"
"  {event_team}\n"
"- You can review proposals here:\n"
"  {event_review}\n"
"- And create your schedule here, once you have accepted proposals:\n"
"  {event_schedule}\n"
msgstr ""
"Hej,\n"
"\n"
"vi skriver for at informere om, at Call for Participation nu er\n"
"lukket. Her er en liste med links, som kan være nyttige de næste dage:\n"
"\n"
"- Her finder du en liste over alle dine {submission_count} forslag:\n"
"  {event_submissions}\n"
"- Her kan du tilføje bedømmere:\n"
"  {event_team}\n"
"- Her kan du bedømme forslag:\n"
"  {event_review}\n"
"- Og oprette dit program her, når du har accepteret forslag:\n"
"  {event_schedule}\n"

#: base/models/settings.py:112
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"congratulations, your event is over! Hopefully it went well. Here are some\n"
"statistics you might find interesting:\n"
"\n"
"- You had {submission_count} proposals,\n"
"- Of which you selected {talk_count} sessions.\n"
"- The reviewers wrote {review_count} reviews.\n"
"- You released {schedule_count} schedules in total.\n"
"- Over the course of the event, you sent {mail_count} mails.\n"
"\n"
"If there is anything you’re missing, please contact us via our website on "
"eventyay.com.\n"
msgstr ""
"Hej,\n"
"\n"
"tillykke, dit arrangement er slut! Forhåbentlig gik det godt. Her er nogle\n"
"statistikker, som du måske finder interessante:\n"
"\n"
"- Du havde {submission_count} forslag,\n"
"- hvoraf du valgte {talk_count} sessioner.\n"
"- Bedømmerne skrev {review_count} bedømmelser.\n"
"- Du udgav {schedule_count} tidsplaner i alt.\n"
"- I løbet af arrangementet sendte du {mail_count} mails.\n"
"\n"
"Hvis der er noget, der mangler, kan du kontakte os via vores hjemmeside på "
"eventyay.com.\n"

