#: base/views/errors.py:21
msgid ""
"You are seeing this message because this HTTPS site requires a 'Referer "
"header' to be sent by your Web browser, but none was sent. This header is "
"required for security reasons, to ensure that your browser is not being "
"hijacked by third parties."
msgstr ""
"Denne meddelelse vises, fordi dette HTTPS-websted kræver, at der sendes en "
"'Referer'-header fra webbrowseren, men der blev ikke sendt nogen. Denne "
"header er påkrævet af sikkerhedshensyn for at sikre, at browseren ikke "
"bliver overtaget af tredjeparter."

#: base/views/errors.py:27
msgid ""
"If you have configured your browser to disable 'Referer' headers, please re-"
"enable them, at least for this site, or for HTTPS connections, or for 'same-"
"origin' requests."
msgstr ""
"Hvis browseren er konfigureret til at deaktivere 'Referer'-headere, skal de "
"aktiveres igen, i det mindste for dette websted eller for HTTPS-forbindelser "
"eller for 'same-origin'-anmodninger."

#: base/views/errors.py:33
msgid ""
"You are seeing this message because this site requires a CSRF cookie when "
"submitting forms. This cookie is required for security reasons, to ensure "
"that your browser is not being hijacked by third parties."
msgstr ""
"Denne meddelelse vises, fordi dette websted kræver en CSRF-cookie ved "
"indsendelse af formularer. Denne cookie er påkrævet af sikkerhedsmæssige "
"årsager for at sikre, at browseren ikke bliver overtaget af tredjeparter."

#: base/views/errors.py:39
msgid ""
"If you have configured your browser to disable cookies, please re-enable "
"them, at least for this site, or for 'same-origin' requests."
msgstr ""
"Hvis browseren er konfigureret til at deaktivere cookies, skal de aktiveres "
"igen, i det mindste for dette websted eller for forespørgsler med \"same-"
"origin\"."

#: base/views/tasks.py:141
msgid "An unexpected error has occurred, please try again later."
msgstr "Der opstod en uventet fejl. Prøv igen senere."

#: base/views/tasks.py:144
msgid "The task has been completed."
msgstr "Opgaven er fuldført."

#: cfp/flow.py:419
msgid ""
"Your draft was saved. You can continue to edit it as long as the CfP is open."
msgstr "Udkastet blev gemt. Redigering kan fortsætte, så længe CfP er åben."

#: cfp/flow.py:426
msgid ""
"Congratulations, you’ve submitted your proposal! You can continue to make "
"changes to it up to the submission deadline, and you will be notified of any "
"changes or questions."
msgstr ""
"Tillykke – forslaget er indsendt! Det er muligt at foretage ændringer frem "
"til indsendelsesfristen, og der gives besked om eventuelle ændringer eller "
"spørgsmål."

#: cfp/flow.py:454
msgid "Hey, nice to meet you!"
msgstr "Hej, rart at møde dig!"

#: cfp/flow.py:459
msgid ""
"We’re glad that you want to contribute to our event with your proposal. "
"Let’s get started, this won’t take long."
msgstr ""
"Det er dejligt, at der ønskes at bidrage til arrangementet med et forslag. "
"Lad os komme i gang – det tager ikke lang tid."

#: cfp/flow.py:491
msgid ""
"There was an error when logging in. Please contact the organizer for further "
"help."
msgstr ""
"Der opstod en fejl under login. Kontakt arrangøren for yderligere hjælp."

