#: cfp/flow.py:501
msgid "That’s it about your proposal! We now just need a way to contact you."
msgstr ""
"Det var alt om forslaget. Der mangler nu blot en måde at kontakte dig på."

#: cfp/flow.py:506
msgid ""
"To create your proposal, you need an account on this page. This not only "
"gives us a way to contact you, it also gives you the possibility to edit "
"your proposal or to view its current state."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette et forslag kræves en konto på denne side. Det giver en måde "
"at kontakte dig på og mulighed for at redigere forslaget eller se dets "
"aktuelle status."

#: cfp/flow.py:549
#: eventyay_common/templates/eventyay_common/sessions/sessions.html:36
msgid "Profile"
msgstr "Profil"

#: cfp/flow.py:553
msgid "Tell us something about yourself!"
msgstr "Fortæl noget om dig selv!"

#: cfp/flow.py:558
msgid ""
"This information will be publicly displayed next to your session - you can "
"always edit for as long as proposals are still open."
msgstr ""
"Disse oplysninger vises offentligt ved siden af din session – de kan altid "
"redigeres, så længe forslag stadig er åbne."

#: cfp/phrases.py:7
msgid "Go to CfP"
msgstr "Gå til CfP"

#: cfp/phrases.py:10
msgid ""
"If we know a user by this email address (who has not requested a password "
"reset in the last 24 hours), we will send you an email containing further "
"instructions. If you don’t see the email within the next minutes, check your "
"spam inbox!"
msgstr ""
"Hvis der findes en bruger med denne e-mailadresse (som ikke har anmodet om "
"nulstilling af adgangskode inden for de seneste 24 timer), sendes en e-mail "
"med yderligere instruktioner. Hvis e-mailen ikke ses inden for de næste "
"minutter, så tjek spamindbakken."

#: cfp/phrases.py:14
msgid ""
"This link was not valid. Make sure you copied the complete URL from the "
"email and that the email is no more than 24 hours old."
msgstr ""
"Dette link var ikke gyldigt. Kontrollér, at den fulde URL blev kopieret fra "
"e-mailen, og at e-mailen ikke er mere end 24 timer gammel."

#: cfp/phrases.py:17
msgid "Awesome! You can now log in using your new password."
msgstr "Perfekt! Log nu ind med den nye adgangskode."

#: cfp/phrases.py:19
msgid "Your proposal has been withdrawn."
msgstr "Dit forslag er blevet trukket tilbage."

#: cfp/phrases.py:21
msgid ""
"Your proposal can’t be withdrawn at this time – please contact us if you "
"need to withdraw your proposal!"
msgstr ""
"Forslaget kan ikke trækkes tilbage lige nu – kontakt os, hvis der er behov "
"for at trække forslaget tilbage."

#: cfp/phrases.py:23
msgid "Your session has been confirmed – we’re looking forward to seeing you!"
