#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/submission_base.html:83
msgid ""
"You can save your proposal as a draft and submit it later. Organisers will "
"not be able to see your proposal, though they will be able to send you "
"reminder emails about the upcoming deadline."
msgstr ""
"Forslaget kan gemmes som kladde og indsendes senere. Arrangører vil ikke "
"kunne se forslaget, men vil kunne sende påmindelsesmail om den kommende "
"deadline."

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/submission_base.html:100
msgid "You need to be logged in to submit a proposal"
msgstr "Der skal være logget ind for at indsende et forslag"

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/submission_base.html:101
msgid ""
"Please log in or create an account to submit a proposal. This enables us to "
"contact you and allows you to edit your proposal or check its status at any "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Log ind eller opret en konto for at indsende et forslag. Det gør det muligt "
"at kontakte dig og giver mulighed for at redigere forslaget eller tjekke "
"status når som helst."

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/submission_questions.html:13
msgid "… about your proposal:"
msgstr "… om forslaget:"

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/submission_questions.html:21
msgid "… about yourself:"
msgstr "… om dig selv:"

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/submission_user.html:9
msgid "Sign in or register to save your draft"
msgstr "Log ind eller registrer for at gemme dit kladdeudkast"

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/submission_user.html:18
msgid ""
"Organisers will not be able to see your draft or your email address. They "
"will be able to send you reminders about your pending proposal draft closer "
"to the deadline."
msgstr ""
"Arrangørerne kan ikke se dit kladdeudkast eller din mailadresse. De kan "
"sende dig påmindelser om dit afventende kladdeudkast tættere på deadline."

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_mails.html:4
#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_mails.html:7
msgid "Your Emails"
msgstr "Dine mails"

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_mails.html:9
msgid ""
"These are emails the organisers sent you, so you should be able to find them "
"in your email inbox, but this page serves as a helper in case your email "
"address was unavailable or the emails got lost in some way."
msgstr ""
"Dette er mails, som arrangørerne har sendt til dig, så du bør kunne finde "
"dem i din mailindbakke, men denne side fungerer som hjælp, hvis din "
"mailadresse ikke var tilgængelig, eller hvis mailsene på en eller anden måde "
"blev væk."

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_profile.html:5
#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_profile.html:14
msgid "Your Profile"
msgstr "Din profil"

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_profile.html:16
msgid ""
"This data will be displayed publicly if your proposal is accepted. It is "
"also visible to reviewers."
msgstr ""
"Disse data vises offentligt, hvis dit forslag bliver accepteret. De er også "
"synlige for bedømmere."

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_profile.html:36
msgid "We have some questions"
msgstr "Der er nogle spørgsmål"

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_submission_confirm.html:20
msgid "Congratulations on your acceptance!"
msgstr "Tillykke med din accept!"

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_submission_confirm.html:24
msgid ""
"Please provide us with your available hours during the event, so that we can "
"schedule your event accordingly:"
msgstr ""
"Angiv venligst dine tilgængelige timer under arrangementet, så arrangementet "
"kan planlægges derefter:"

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_submission_confirm.html:40
msgid ""
"By confirming your proposal, you agree that you are able and willing to "
"participate in this event and present the content of this proposal. The "
"proposal data, such as title, abstract, description, and any uploads you "
"provided, can be made publicly available once the proposal is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Ved at bekræfte dit forslag accepteres det, at du kan og vil deltage i dette "
"arrangement og præsentere indholdet i dette forslag. Forslagsdata, såsom "
"titel, resumé, beskrivelse og eventuelle uploads, kan gøres offentligt "
"tilgængelige, når forslaget er bekræftet."

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_submission_confirm.html:50
#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_submission_edit.html:122
#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/user_submission_withdraw.html:23
