msgid "Move a BBB room to a new server"
msgstr "Flyt et BBB-rum til en ny server"

#: control/templates/control/bbb_moveroom.html:11
msgid ""
"Moving a room will try to kick everyone out of the room. People need to re-"
"join by reloading the page. If kicking people fails (i.e. server down), it "
"will still proceed, but might create a \"split\" room, i.e. two groups of "
"people who think they are in the same room but are not. Recordings of the "
"room will be no longer accessible through the interface later. It is "
"recommended to join the room yourself to be able to react to this. Use with "
"caution."
msgstr ""
"Flytning af et rum vil forsøge at smide alle ud af rummet. Deltagere skal "
"deltage igen ved at genindlæse siden. Hvis det ikke lykkes at smide "
"deltagere ud (f.eks. hvis serveren er nede), fortsætter flytningen stadig, "
"men kan oprette et „splittet“ rum, dvs. to grupper af deltagere, som tror, "
"de er i samme rum, men ikke er det. Optagelser af rummet vil ikke længere "
"være tilgængelige via brugerfladen senere. Det anbefales at deltage i rummet "
"selv for at kunne reagere på dette. Brug med forsigtighed."

#: control/templates/control/bbb_moveroom.html:14
msgid "Move"
