#: plugins/banktransfer/payment.py:35
msgid ""
"I have understood that people will pay the ticket price directly to my bank "
"account and eventyay cannot automatically know what payments arrived. "
"Therefore, I will either mark payments as complete manually, or regularly "
"import a digital bank statement in order to give eventyay the required "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Det er forstået, at deltagere betaler billetprisen direkte til bankkontoen, "
"og at eventyay ikke automatisk kan registrere, hvilke betalinger der er "
"modtaget. Derfor vil betalinger enten blive markeret som gennemført manuelt "
"eller der vil regelmæssigt blive importeret et digitalt kontoudtog for at "
"give eventyay de nødvendige oplysninger."

